<p>Shining City</h1></p>

<p>From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</p>


<ref class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</ref>
<ref class="mw-jump-link" href="#p-search">Jump to search</ref>
<p>Shining City is a play by <ref target="/wiki/Conor_McPherson" title="Conor McPherson">Conor McPherson</ref>, set in <ref target="/wiki/Dublin" title="Dublin">Dublin</ref>, which was first performed in the <ref target="/wiki/West_End_theatre" title="West End theatre">West End</ref> in 2004.</p>

